Changes made:
  The guide's written material was restructured, rewritten, and visualized as
  an interactive web course — modules, rendered diagrams, practice exercises,
  and original exam-style quiz questions. This is an unofficial study aid and
  is not affiliated with, authorized, or endorsed by Anthropic.

